  "description": "DHCP Server monitoring dashboard. Displays scope utilization, message rates (discovers, offers, requests, ACKs, NAKs), lease activity trends, and service health for all monitored Windows DHCP servers. Metrics sourced from Grafana Alloy via prometheus.exporter.windows dhcp collector.",
